item.title: My runserver is fucked up
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

[quote=“kill you704, post:6, topic:399543”][quote author=zyle1992 link=topic=496672.msg3631521#msg3631521 date=1308259447]

If you use uTorrent just make it a random port then open run.bat then while still open! Go back to uTorrent change port back to 43594 and then close run and reopen. It will then work. If you are using a regular lynx portforwarding manually. Go to ctrl + alt + del and click start task manager go to processes and find out what is running under java. End the process re run run.bat and it should work. Gl.

He already said he fixed it.
[/quote]
Uhm… No he didn’t.[/quote][quote=“ganter, post:3, topic:399543”]yeah ur rigth… my other server was running.[/quote]

orly?
